  "prompt": "Is this considered a four pack?",
  "response": "To determine if something is considered a four pack, we need to know the quantity of items contained within the package. A four pack typically means that the package contains four individual items. \n\nFor example:\n- A four pack of beverages would contain four bottles or cans.\n- A four pack of batteries would contain four batteries.\n\nIf you can provide more details about the specific item you are referring to, I can give you a more precise answer. For instance, you could tell me what the product is and how many units are included in the package.",
